title1: Indian scientists design mask that is self-disinfecting, breathable and biodegradable - The Financial Express
description1: To make wearing masks more convenient a team of Indian scientists have developed a self-disinfecting antiviral mask to fight the disease. The mask is coated with copper-based nanoparticles that are more potent to restrict foreign particles like viral and bacterial infections as well as coronavirus, the science and technology ministry said. The mask is also washable, highly breathable, low cost and biodegradable.
